==Afrikaans==

===Etymology===
From {{inh|af|nl|pond}}, from {{inh|af|dum|pont}}, {{m|dum|pond}}, from {{inh|af|odt|punt}}, from {{inh|af|gem-pro|*pundą|t=pound, weight}}, borrowed from {{der|af|la|pondō}}.

===Pronunciation===
