====Usage notes====
Used in linguistic descriptions in Finnish. For example, a Finnish grammar could use {{m-lite|fi||-mA}} to refer to the suffix {{m-lite|fi|-ma}} (in e.g. {{m-lite|fi|osuma}}) or {{m-lite|fi|-mä}} (in e.g. {{m-lite|fi|elämä}}).

